metadata.name: Alice in Wonderland #1
metadata.description:
The bizarre beauty of Alice, who seems to exist in a dream landscape, has been continuously accumulated in the new world of expression that the artist is advancing little by little. Although they are drawing the same material, more powerful strokes appear through long-time worries about expression techniques and simple brush strokes, and the colors add mystery. Alice in Wonderland, completed with beautiful colors and powerful strokes, leads the audience into a strange space.
